# UI/UX Guardrails

## Accessibility

- Prefer native semantics (`button`, `a`, `label`, `table`) before adding ARIA.
- Ensure visible focus (`:focus-visible`) and full keyboard support for interactive UI.
- Icon-only buttons must include an accessible label (`aria-label` or visible text).

